{
  "texts": [
    "This particular tool allows not only the annotation of documents with specific ontologies but also their download and can be linked to the other tools in the chain to provide more complex functionalities.",
    "The upload interfaces are similar to those of the BPMN annotator tool.",
    "For more information on this specific part of the toolchain, see Sect. 5.4.",
    "• An Expert System applies logical rules to the annotated BPMNs and documents, either to derive new knowledge to be stored as part of the knowledge base, or to validate them and verify specific standards applied in the domain.",
    "Sect. 5.6 provides more details on this specific tool."
  ]
}